>> Hello everybody !
>> 
>> Is there a syntax driven editing tool for caml and ocaml (ctcaml/ctocaml) ?

CtCaml is available through:

http://www.inria.fr/croap/ctcaml/ctcaml-eng.html


CtCaml is a programming environment for CamlLight. Its main 
characteristic is that it makes use of type information.
The environment is experimental still and only CtCaml is
supported.






